Original concept and project direction: Domingo Moreno / DoTwo.

This project was created to provide a practical local video conversion
workflow for audiovisual labs, with K2/XDCAM and H.264 export profiles,
inspection, trimming, and queue-based processing.

Initial implementation and tooling were developed with OpenClaw/Bender
assistance.

